<div class="post">
<div class="inner" id="msg_790568">xiu地一下把人丢出去<br>你能勉强举起冰箱但是丢出去的话也造成不了什么伤害的。<br><br><br><strong>投掷伤害表</strong><br><br><strong>投掷物重量</strong>&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;<strong>伤害值</strong><br>BL/8或以下&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; 击打, -2 每d<br>BL/4或以下&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; 击打, -1 每d<br>BL/2或以下&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; 击打<br>BL或以下&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;击打, +1 每d<br>2xBL或以下&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; 击打<br>4xBL或以下&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;击打, -1/2 每d（去掉分数）<br>8xBL或以下&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;击打, -1 每d<br><br><br><br><br><br>顺便附<strong>投掷距离表</strong><br><br></div>
